{{Infobox brain|Name=底丘脑|Latin=|Image=Anatomie-Basalganglien-A.jpg|Caption=|Image2=|Caption2=|IsPartOf=|Components=|Artery=|Vein=}}'''底丘脑'''（英文：Subthalamus）是[[间脑|间脑]]的一部分，位于间脑的最底部。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Subthalamus - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/subthalamus#:~:text=The%20subthalamus%20is%20the%20most,posterior%20part%20of%20the%20diencephalon.|accessdate=2021-04-03|work=|publisher=ScienceDirect|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=底丘脑|url=https://www.imaios.com/cn/e-Anatomy/node_322323/node_313668|accessdate=2021-04-03|work=IMAIOS|language=cn}}</ref> 底丘脑与{{le|苍白球|Globus pallidus}}（大脑的一个[[基底核|基底核]]）相连。<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wlGDPwz_7KoC&q=+subthalamus+part+%22globus+pallidus%22&pg=PA211|title=Theme atlas of anatomy: head and neuroanathomy|isbn=9781588904416|last1=Schünke|first1=Michael|last2=Ross|first2=Lawrence M.|last3=Schulte|first3=Erik|last4=Lamperti|first4=Edward D.|last5=Schumacher|first5=Udo|year=2007|access-date=2021-04-03|archive-date=2021-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210828175526/https://books.google.com/books?id=wlGDPwz_7KoC&q=+subthalamus+part+%22globus+pallidus%22&pg=PA211|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 结构 ==
底丘脑位于[[丘脑|丘脑]]的下部（位于丘脑和[[中脑|中脑]]之间）、{{le|内囊|Internal capsule}}内侧、[[下丘脑|下丘脑]]外侧。底丘脑由数个[[灰质|灰质核]]及其附属[[白质|白质]]结构组成<ref name=":0" />：

* {{le|底丘脑核|Subthalamic nucleus}}（底丘脑中最大的结构）<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=底丘脑核|url=https://www.imaios.com/cn/e-Anatomy/node_322323/node_313791|accessdate=2021-04-03|work=IMAIOS|language=cn}}</ref>
* {{le|未定区|Zona incerta}}
* {{le|底丘脑束|Subthalamic fasciculus}}
* {{le|福雷尔区|Fields of Forel}}
* {{le|豆状核袢|Ansa lenticularis}}

== 功能 ==
底丘脑与[[端脑|端脑]]（[[大脑|大脑]]）中的[[纹状体|纹状体]]、间脑中的背侧丘脑、中脑中的{{le|红核|Red nucleus}}及[[黑质|黑质]]之间有[[传出神经纤维|传出性连接]]。此外，底丘脑也与纹状体和黑质之间有[[传入神经纤维|传入性连接]]。底丘脑有整合躯体运动的功能，如果受损可能造成某些运动障碍。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The subthalamic nucleus in the context of movement disorders|url=https://doi.org/10.1093/brain/awh029|last=Hamani|first=Clement|last2=Saint‐Cyr|first2=Jean A.|date=2004-01-01|journal=Brain|issue=1|doi=10.1093/brain/awh029|volume=127|pages=4–20|issn=0006-8950|last3=Fraser|first3=Justin|last4=Kaplitt|first4=Michael|last5=Lozano|first5=Andres M.}}</ref>

